T02TD3325E:20b-0: @20b # // h'um gi sa bon las skyes nas //
T02TD3325E:20b-1: rnam par dag par bya ba'i bar du'o //
T02TD3325E:20b-2: de nas nyi ma la gnas pa'i yi ge h'um yongs su gyur pa'i gshin rje mthar byed khro ba dang bcas pa skra gyen du 'greng pa /
T02TD3325E:20b-5: zhabs drug pa ma he la zhon pa /
T02TD3325E:20b-6: g-yon brkyang ba'i zhabs kyis gnas pa /
T02TD3325E:20b-7: mi'i mgo bo'i phreng bas rnam par brgyan pa /
T02TD3325E:20b-8: shin tu 'jigs par byed pa'i rnam pa can /
T02TD3325E:20b-9: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can /
T02TD3325E:20b-10: g-yas pa na ral gri dang /
T02TD3325E:20b-13: g-yon pa na dril bu dang /
T02TD3325E:20b-16: dbu rgyan mi bskyod pa'i rnam par bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3325E:20b-17: de nas dam tshig gi phyag rgya bcing bar bya'o //
T02TD3325E:20b-18: thal mo sbyar ba bcings te /
T02TD3325E:20b-19: mtheb chen gnyis kha phye ste sdigs mdzub gnyis kyang kha phye zhing gung mo gnyis tshigs gsum pa bcag par bya'o //
T02TD3325E:20b-20: aom hr'i:shtr'i:bi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3325E:20b-21: zhes bya ba'i bzlas ba bya'o //
T02TD3325E:20b-22: gshin rje nag po'i sgrub pa'i thabs rdzogs so //
T02TD3325E:20b-23: khams pa lo ts'a ba ba ri dge slong dharma k'irtis bsgyur ba'o /
